      "content": "it doesn't feel like a setback though. it feels like everything is just... stuck. the shame is constant. every time I close my eyes I just see the look on their faces. rebuilding sounds like a fantasy, like i'm supposed to just pretend this didn't happen and keep pretending to be the person i was. but that person is dead. there's nothing left to rebuild.",
