      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't want to \"live with it.\" i don't want to spend the next ten years just trying to slowly manage this crushing weight and feeling like a ghost of who i used to be. it feels more like a life sentence than a lesson. i just want the noise to stop. i want the shame to finally be over.",
